      <title>博利登将在劳资协议达成后重启欧洲最大锌矿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/boliden-to-reopen-europe-s-largest-zinc-mine-after-labor-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Boliden AB 与工会达成协议后，将于今年晚些时候重新开放其爱尔兰锌矿，该协议将降低成本，但将劳动力削减三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/boliden-to-reopen-europe-s-largest-zinc-mine-after-labor-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:52:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
